{{Quote|My loyal bodyguard. You can see why I took off.|[[Thrackan Sal-Solo]] to [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]]|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Ylesia">''[[The New Jedi Order: Ylesia]]''</ref>}}
The '''Ylesian Presidential Guard''' was the official bodyguard of the [[President of Ylesia|President]] of the [[Ylesian Republic]]. Their [[Commander/Legends|commander]] was a [[Duros/Legends|Duros]].

When [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]] was President of [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]], the Guards were given the weapons of the [[Warrior caste]] used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], including [[amphistaff]]s and [[Vonduun Skerr Kyrric|vonduun crab armor]]. However, the armor kept biting the Yelesian guards, so they switched to a laminite version of the armor. They also had trouble mastering the commands of the amphistaff, and several Brigaders had injured themselves trying to control the [[biot]]s.

When [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commander]] [[Maal Lah]] arrived to bring the troops to standard, he inspected the Presidential Guard. The mere sight of them made him long for his kinsman, [[Czulkang Lah]], to whip them&mdash;literally&mdash;into shape. Sal-Solo whole-heartedly agreed, and actually had [[Dagga Marl]] provide for his protection.

